visual_description.name: parked_tour_bus_on_gravel_path.jpg
visual_description.description: Large tour bus parked on gravel path, side door open, partial reflection of trees. Bright daylight, clear sky. Image tilted, slightly cut-off framing. Minor glare on bus windows.
visual_description.score_basis: Standard tour bus photo in natural light. Image slightly tilted, open door adds casual feel. Colors clear but some glare/reflections on windows. Framing cuts off front of bus. No obvious digital manipulation.
